<title>USA: Edison Brothers Stores Inc Q4 Feb 1 loss.</title>
<headline>Edison Brothers Stores Inc Q4 Feb 1 loss.</headline>
<dateline>ST. LOUIS, Mo. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr     loss	     $4.00     loss	 $4.83</p>
<p> Net     loss	    88,800     loss     106,600</p>
<p> Revs		     308,200		  416,800</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  22,202		   22,087</p>
<p>(All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Current Q4 loss after $84.5 million in special charges, including $74.0 million for loss on long-lived assets and $10.5 million in restructuring and reorganization charges. Year-ago Q4 after $97.8 million in special charges.  </p>
<p>			YEAR</p>
<p> Shr     loss	     $6.46     loss	$10.06</p>
