<p> Revs		   1,090,400		1,389,400</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  22,185		   22,070</p>
<p>(All Data Above 000s Except Per Share Numbers)</p>
<p>NOTE: Current full-year loss after $110.3 million of special charges, including $74.0 million for impaired assets and $36.3 million in restructuring and reorganization expenses. Excluding special charges, current full year loss was $32.9 million.</p>
<p>Year-ago loss after $167.1 million in special charges. Excluding charges, year-ago loss was $63.9 million.</p>
